		<h2>Gamification</h2>
		<p>Boost engagement with cutting-edge gamification features like avatars, badges, leaderboards, experience points, achievements, and rewards.</p>
	</div>
	<div id="feature_2">
		<h2>Learning Management</h2>
		<p>Design robust courses with announcements, notifications, forums, file storage, tasks, and gradebooks.</p>
	</div>
	<div id="feature_3">
		<h2>Task Organizer</h2>
		<p>Stay organized with an integrated to do list for course work and timely notifications for tasks and announcements.</p>
	</div>
	<div id="feature_4">
		<h2>Learning Analytics</h2>
		<p>Improve learning with detailed feedback on course outcomes and grades, personalized statistics for each course, and recommendations for peer mentoring.</p>
	</div>
	<div id="feature_5">
		<h2>Social Media</h2>
		<p>Build community and increase retention with social media features like profiles, groups, friends, status updates, and messaging.</p>
	</div>
	<a href="/users/sign_up" class="big_orangebtn">Try a demo</a>
